700164f-b.text:
E. 161st Street, east from the Macombs Dam Bridge ramp (east of Jerome Avenue). On the right is a portion of the Yankee Stadlum, and straddling 16lst Street is the elevated station of the IRT subway. In the right background is the Bronx County Court House and to its left is the Concourse Plaza Hotel, both on the Grand Concourse. View 2 is east from
Cromwell Avenue.
P.L. Sperr  April 10, 1941
NO REPRODUCTI0NS  Views 1,2
